                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-98-off524 t18030420-98-cd525"></join>, a pair of sheets, value 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18030420-98-victim796" type="victimName">
                     Judah 
